title: If there is no data for a series, a friendly error message should be displayed
OB: When attempting to preview the series, no friendly error message is displayed.
EB: I expect a friendly error message to be displayed when there is no data for a series.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Open the preview of a series. 2. Ensure there is no data available for the series. 3. Note that no friendly error message is displayed.
